t=E2=80=99s what he wants =E2=80=94=C2=A0at least, what he wants in the mom=
ent =E2=80=94=C2=A0so he does it. =E2=80=9CMusk is just a being of pure imp=
ulse,=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/299=
