<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But I am also drawn to two weirder and more co=
nvoluted theories<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-5" style=3D"=
color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px;=
 border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; backgr=
ound-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[5]</span>
</a>:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Tesla Inc. stock is the main source of=
 Musk=E2=80=99s wealth, and he has done a good job of maximizing that stock=
=E2=80=99s price by rallying a legion of retail fans. But eventually he nee=
ds to cash out, and that presents a problem: If the founder, chief executiv=
e officer and cult leader of Tesla starts dumping stock, then that signals =
a loss of confidence, and the stock would collapse before he could get much=
 money out of it. But if he created a=C2=A0<em>distraction</em>, or an=C2=
=A0<em>excuse</em>, for dumping the stock, then that might cushion the blow=
. Not =E2=80=9CI am selling $40 billion of Tesla stock to top-tick it=E2=80=
=9D but more like =E2=80=9CI am selling $40 billion of Tesla stock to buy T=
witter and wage war for the future of civilization.=E2=80=9D Then his fans =
might say =E2=80=9Cgreat, sell that stock, wage that war,=E2=80=9D and he c=
an sell stock without taking too much of a hit. And in fact Musk <em>has=C2=
=A0</em><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29993996.2=
61528/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTItMTUvZ=
Wxvbi1tdXNrLXNlbGxzLWF0LWxlYXN0LTMtNi1iaWxsaW9uLW9mLXRlc2xhLXNoYXJlcz9jbXBp=
ZD1CQkQxMjE1MjJfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2x=
ldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMjEyMTUmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cB576e3658" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">sold almost $40 billion of Tesla stock</a>, a=
fter repeatedly promising that he was done. We have <a href=3D"https://link=
.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29993996.261528/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZ=
XJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDQtMjgvZWxvbi1tdXNrLXMtb3RoZXItbWVy=
