 and (2) he has plowed most of the proceeds into buying Twitter, which has =
probably gone down even more! I do not see how he has accomplished any real=
 diversification or stock-price-maintenance goals.=C2=A0</li>=09<li style=
=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Tesla Inc. is the main source of Musk=E2=80=99s we=
alth, and his main goal in life is selling lots of Teslas. He has sold all =
the Teslas that he can sell to coastal elite liberals, and now he faces the=
