<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThere is no TSLA CEO today,=E2=80=9D =
Gary Black, managing partner of the Future Fund LLC, which owns roughly $50=
 million worth of Tesla, tweeted Monday. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Mr. Black said, =E2=80=9CThe market voted toda=
